author: CNET
description: Toilet time is getting even more useful and insightful. A few months ago Withings officially released U-Scan, the first toilet plug-in urine scanner. It’s pretty much a mini health analysis lab in your home that gives you results on your phone. The U-Scan Nutrio can help you track your hydration, nutrition, calcium trends, and more. Let’s unbox it and set it up. #withings #healthtracker #healthtracking #urinetests #healthtech
title: Unboxing The First Toilet Plug-In Urine Scanner 🚽

author: CNET
description:
Two folding phones made it to our top mobile phone picks of 2025: the Samsung Galaxy Z Fold 7 and the Motorola Razr Ultra. They even both won CNET Editors’ Choice Awards. 

Here’s senior writer @abraralheeti and managing editor @directedbypatrick to walk us through their choices. #mobile #foldable #samsung #motorola
title: Why Two Of Our Favorite Phones of 2025 Are Foldables
